        "subject": "You've received a loan request from user who saw you on our website!",
        "contentType": "text/html",
        "contentValue": "=<html>  <head>   <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />   <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />   <title>Document</title>   <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Work+Sans:400,500,600,700,800,900&display=swap\"     rel=\"stylesheet\" />   <style>     html,     body {       margin: 0;       padding: 0;     }      table {       border: 0;       border-spacing: 0;       border-collapse: collapse;     }      @media screen and (max-width: 520px) {       h1.header {         font-size: 24px !important;         line-height: 24px !important;       }     }   </style> </head>  <body width=\"100%\" style=\"width: 100%; background: #eaeaea\" bgcolor=\"#F1F3F5\">   <center>     <table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\"       style=\"width: 95%; max-width: 600px\">       <tr>         <td class=\"email-container\">           <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 50px auto\">             <!--- Logo: START -->             <tr>               <td style=\"padding: 20px\">                 <a href=\"#\">                   <img                       src=\"https://lsq.li/lendsqr-long-logo\"                       border=\"0\"                       height=\"30\"                       style=\"display: block\"                     />                 </a>               </td>             </tr>             <!--- Logo: END -->             <!--- Header: START -->             <tr>               <td>                </td>             </tr>             <!--- Header: END -->              <!--- Body: START -->             <tr>               <td style=\"                     font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;                     font-size: 16px;                     line-height: 150%;                     color: rgb(45, 46, 46);                     background-color: #fff;                     border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;                     padding: 50px 50px;                   \">                   <h2 style=\"                       font-size: 35px;                       font-family: Degular Display, Arial, sans-serif;                       line-height: 110%;                     \">                   {{ $json.borrower_name }} has requested for a {{ $json['Loan amount'] }} loan                 </h2>                  <p><b>\ud83d\udc4b\ud83c\udfff Hi {{ $json.org_name }} Team,</b></p>                  <p>                   You've got a new borrower from Project X \u2013 our lender directory where thousands of borrowers come                   looking for loans. {{ $json.borrower_name }} just applied and specifically chose your organization.                 </p>                  <!-- REQUEST DETAILS TABLE -->                 <p>                 <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"                   style=\"width: 100%; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px;\">                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Name                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                       {{ $json.borrower_name }}                    </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Email                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                      {{ $json.borrower_email }}                   </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Phone                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                      {{ $json.borrower_phone }}                     </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Loan amount                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                         {{ $json['Loan amount'] }}                </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Purpose                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                       {{ $json.loan_purpose }}                </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Tenor                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                       {{ $json.Tenor }}             </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td                       style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       City                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">                       {{ $json.city }}                  </td>                   </tr>                   <tr>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-weight: 600; width: 35%;\">                       Country                     </td>                     <td style=\"padding: 12px;\">                        {{ $json.country }}                    </td>                   </tr>                 </table>                 </p>               </td>             </tr>             <!--- Body: END -->              <!--- Footer: START -->             <tr>               <td style=\"                     font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;                     font-size: 12px;                     line-height: 22px;                     color: #334a6a;                     opacity: 0.6;                     padding: 50px;                     padding-top: 20px;                     /* border-top: 1px solid rgba(17, 41, 69, 0.1); */                     border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;                     background-color: #fff;                   \">                 <p style=\"margin: 0; width: 100%\">                   <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This request was submitted through our lender directory. We have not verified the borrower's information or creditworthiness. Please conduct your own due diligence before proceeding with any loan application. If you need more details, you can reach out to us via email at          <a href=\"mailto:support@lendsqr.com\">support@lendsqr.com</a>.                 </p>                  <a href=\"{{unsubscribe_link}}\">Click here to unsubscribe</a>               </td>             </tr>             <!--- Footer: END -->           </table>         </td>       </tr>     </table>   </center> </body>  </html>",
