        "contentValue": "=<html>\n\n<head>\n\t<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n\t<title>Document</title>\n\t<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Work+Sans:400,500,600,700,800,900&display=swap\"\n\t\trel=\"stylesheet\" />\n\t<style>\n\t\thtml,\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tmargin: 0;\n\t\t\tpadding: 0;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\ttable {\n\t\t\tborder: 0;\n\t\t\tborder-spacing: 0;\n\t\t\tborder-collapse: collapse;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t@media screen and (max-width: 520px) {\n\t\t\th1.header {\n\t\t\t\tfont-size: 24px !important;\n\t\t\t\tline-height: 24px !important;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t</style>\n</head>\n\n<body width=\"100%\" style=\"width: 100%; background: #eaeaea\" bgcolor=\"#F1F3F5\">\n\t<center>\n\t\t<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\"\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 95%; max-width: 600px\">\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td class=\"email-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"width: 100%; margin: 50px auto\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Logo: START -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding: 20px\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"https://lsq.li/lendsqr-long-logo\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tborder=\"0\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\theight=\"30\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tstyle=\"display: block\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Logo: END -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Header: START -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Header: END -->\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Body: START -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfont-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfont-size: 16px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tline-height: 150%;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcolor: rgb(45, 46, 46);\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbackground-color: #fff;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tborder-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpadding: 50px 50px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>\ud83d\udc4bHi {{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.borrower_name }},</b></p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLast week, you applied for a loan through {{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.org_name }} in\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tour directory. We're checking in because we care about how\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthis turned out for you.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Did {{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.org_name }} reach out to you?</b></p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u2705 If yes \u2013 That's great! We hope the process is going\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsmoothly.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u274c If not \u2013 Please let us know. We can follow up on your\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbehalf or connect you with an alternative lender if needed.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEither way, we'd love to know so we can keep improving the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\texperience.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSimply reply to this email with an update so we can assist\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tyou better.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Body: END -->\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Footer: START -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfont-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfont-size: 12px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tline-height: 22px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcolor: #334a6a;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\topacity: 0.6;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpadding: 50px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpadding-top: 20px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t/* border-top: 1px solid rgba(17, 41, 69, 0.1); */\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tborder-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbackground-color: #fff;\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0; width: 100%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Please note:</b> We connected you with this lender\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthrough our directory, but we are not involved in the loan\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tapproval or disbursement process. For updates on your\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tapplication status, please contact the lender directly.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIf you have questions about our directory service or need\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tassistance, please reach out to us at\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"mailto:support@lendsqr.com\">support@lendsqr.com</a>.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"{{unsubscribe_link}}\">Click here to unsubscribe</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--- Footer: END -->\n\t\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t</table>\n\t</center>\n</body>\n\n</html>",
